snippet: A wide assortment of performers gathered in Hearst Plaza on Friday for a concert in memory of Jenneth Webster, who directed Lincoln Center Out of Doors for 28 years.
abstract: Siobhan Burke reviews dance performances at tribute concert to Lincoln Center Out of Doors director Jenneth Webster, who died in April, at Lincoln Center.
lead_paragraph: A wide assortment of performers gathered in Hearst Plaza on Friday for a concert in memory of Jenneth Webster, who directed Lincoln Center Out of Doors for 28 years.
